featuredSessions.description: DevFestYYC is Western Canada's largest Google Cloud and Cloud Native conference. We're bringing Alberta's Startup and Enterprise developers, architects, data scientists, operations professionals and IT decision makers together to learn with world-class cloud experts and top local speakers. Let's Build What’s Next and Transform Legacy. Together.

howItWas.description: With 2 full days of bootcamps, workshops, labs, demos, you’ll advance your expertise in Google Cloud and Cloud Native technology. Master the tools and techniques required to design, architect, develop, scale, launch, integrate and maintain today’s advanced cloud solutions.
howItWas.label: DevFestYYC 2019 is coming!

ticketsBlock.title: Tickets
ticketsBlock.ticketsDetails: Your pass grants you access to all keynotes, technical sessions, hands-on workshops and presentations. You'll also get opportunities to meet and network with speakers and community members. We'll provide non-stop coffee, fun and lunch on both days! Stay tuned for special pop-up events!

team.description:
We are [GDGYYC](https://www.gdgyyc.com/), Calgary's Google Cloud Developer Group. We're here to Build What's Next and Transform Legacy with Google Cloud and Cloud Native technology.
DevFestYYC is bringing Alberta’s Startup and Enterprise developers, architects, data scientists and operations professionals together with world-class and top local speakers.

blocks.title: Organizer
blocks.description: GDGYYC is the proud organizer of DevFestYYC. We’re here to build a world-class developer community in Calgary.

blocks.title: What is GDG?
blocks.description: Google Developers Groups (GDG) are the world's largest network of technologists. GDG chapters can be found in over 1000 cities around the world. GDGs are committed to advancing developer knowledge of Google Cloud and Cloud Native technologies.
